{"tid":2341059,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港人投訴惠州隔離酒店 保安擸棍談判","createTime":"2020-12-26T04:54:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-26T13:26:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"eb90b72aeec1898b82392d13278809ff17afb806","tid":2341059,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:54:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/ODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUprbLZzzsfwfKyNyJagnZM4%3D&h=ceddee09\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201226%2FODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI%2F&h=c341e9d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201226/ODJZJLMHPZFX5GIJBJTYMRLLDI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n港人投訴惠州隔離酒店 保安擸棍談判<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gefqkMlMKclA7ZvxFwesruEsbf4=/1181x1300/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7RER3NCRANDKZFBE3CWCRZMDIA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgefqkMlMKclA7ZvxFwesruEsbf4%3D%2F1181x1300%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7RER3NCRANDKZFBE3CWCRZMDIA.jpg&h=d05df18c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■聯署信指一名女童跌傷流血，惟酒店遲遲不安排她送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n自第四波疫情爆發，港人趁聖誕長假期北上「避疫」過新年的人數陸續增多，有自稱是「愛國愛港大聯盟」的微信公眾號「中港大聯盟」，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：明恩樓突解封 居民轟兒戲  民政處安排亂 區議員接五百投訴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亂收費 房污糟 飯有蟲<br />\n<br />\n「中港大聯盟」的文章指，該封聯署信前日曝光，內容指60多名港人23日到惠州市，在未被告知的情況下被送到龍門縣天然居隔離酒店接受隔離。單日隔離費用為470元人民幣（下同；約558港元），但市內其他隔離酒店收費不超過250元（約297港元）。他們與酒店人員交涉時，酒店負責人大聲吼叫，又有多名保安手持警棍參與談判。其後酒店開始怠慢他們，送餐時間由晚上7時半延遲至9時半之後，飯菜中有昆蟲、帶毛的雞肉，又不准外賣；床單浴袍有污迹、電視無法觀看、暖氣亦有問題。<br />\n<br />\n「有幾位一歲多到四、五歲的孩子，已經兩頓飯沒有吃任何東西了，其中一位甚至摔傷頭部出血，未得到酒店妥善照顧。」據指，該名女童跌倒地上，額頭傷口深，鮮血沾染床單，但酒店一直沒有安排將她送院治理，其母親則坐在地上嚎啕大哭。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：玉蓮臺強檢 居民︰大廈通地罩<br />\n<br />\n上述港人在投訴信中提出兩大訴求，包括希望政府將他們集中轉移至市內其他隔離酒店，如金葉大酒店，因該酒店確認尚有空房；另外強制要求天然居酒店減價，指市區的隔離酒店每晚房價連餐費低於250元，「一個遠離市區1.5小時車程的隔離酒店（天然居）竟然要價470元，這是所有人不能接受的」。惠州市政府尚未回應事件。<br />\n<br />\n微信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N36CxpPzkUzZfeI0qUw6OCn5VDY=/1181x1363/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LAWJ737GIJF3RBFFMKLDT26O74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN36CxpPzkUzZfeI0qUw6OCn5VDY%3D%2F1181x1363%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLAWJ737GIJF3RBFFMKLDT26O74.jpg&h=cc496ebd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■該群港人投訴酒店保安員持警棍恫嚇住客。"},{"pid":"c6dc90d30795e7050224d2b866ec8ca9b503b786","tid":2341059,"uid":21545,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:55:12.000Z","msg":"社會主義鐵拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9579999cb430fe91e37b572a486ca2034d58b2d","tid":2341059,"uid":9193,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:55:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>咁鍾意返大陸吖嗱</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"cab518f4c0ee5cf44e4620c42e12250f8e70214c","tid":2341059,"uid":175540,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"同我打到佢地仆街"},{"pid":"2a206f010f52bdd5160b4cd788395069e77b6dd8","tid":2341059,"uid":4850,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:57:40.000Z","msg":"抵撚死"},{"pid":"976cfc7a56c3d06e75137eca6eaa302b1a879294","tid":2341059,"uid":224533,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:58:06.000Z","msg":"飯盒啲蟲其實係配料，增加蛋白質<br />\n喺支國有飯食已經係皇恩浩蕩<br />\n14億人都係咁食，而家你投訴係咪搞分化"},{"pid":"960020464df37bd902ff9ac3a30a2807f5274bd8","tid":2341059,"uid":267563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T04:58:29.00